## Relay-P12 MCP Server Integration Plan
**Status:** planned
**Tags:** stack:backend
**Depends on:** Relay-P6, Chat-P1

Implement a full MCP (Model Context Protocol) Server on top of existing REST APIs, enabling AI Agents to discover and control AutoForge programmatically.

### Technology Choices

| Option | Decision |
|--------|----------|
| SDK | `rmcp` (official Anthropic Rust SDK) |
| Transport | stdio + HTTP (SSE) |
| Integration | Direct module integration (no HTTP proxy layer) |

### Module Structure

```
backend/src/mcp/
├── mod.rs          # McpServer struct, #[tool] macros
├── tools/
│   ├── chat.rs     # forge_create_session, forge_send_message, ...
│   ├── relay.rs    # forge_start_relay_run, forge_poll_run_phase, ...
│   ├── specs.rs    # forge_read_specs, forge_update_spec, ...
│   ├── config.rs   # forge_list_api_sources, forge_test_api_connection
│   └── system.rs   # forge_get_performance_logs, forge_browse_directory
├── resources/      # forge://specs/{project}, forge://runs/{run_id}
├── prompts/        # Analysis, review, batch-test templates
└── transport.rs    # stdio / HTTP configuration
```

### Tools Registry (30 tools implemented)

**Chat:** `forge_create_session`, `forge_send_message`, `forge_poll_chat_status`, `forge_get_session`, `forge_delete_session`

**Relay:** `forge_start_relay_run`, `forge_poll_run_phase`, `forge_get_run`, `forge_list_runs`, `forge_advance_run`, `forge_submit_handoff`, `forge_resolve_gate`, `forge_batch_start_runs`, `forge_batch_get_results`

**Specs:** `forge_read_specs`, `forge_update_spec`, `forge_list_specs_sections`

**Config:** `forge_list_api_sources`, `forge_test_api_connection`, `forge_open_project`, `forge_close_project`, `forge_get_project_status`

**System:** `forge_read_file`, `forge_write_file`, `forge_browse_directory`, `forge_shell`, `forge_search`, `forge_get_performance_logs`

### Phase Plan

| Phase | Task | Duration | Status |
|-------|------|----------|--------|
| Phase 1 | Backend event emission — `relay_complete`, `RunMetadata` | 2 days | Planned |
| Phase 2 | Chat integration — `ForgeStreamEvent::RelayComplete`, SSE routing | 2 days | Planned |
| Phase 3 | Frontend UI — system message bubble, "View Report" button | 2 days | Planned |
| Phase 4 | Report link — `?report_id=` navigation, Specs highlight | 1 day | Planned |

